            <html:p>Conjugation with the
<fr:link href="/foreign/stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FD/" title="The adjoint triple between presheaves and families" uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FD/" display-uri="https://stevenschaefer.net/sss-00FD/" type="local">adjunction between presheaves and families</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[U \dashv 
\mathrm {Cofree}]]></fr:tex>
lets us induce a later
construction on families from the one on presheaves,
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\rhd _{\mathrm {Fam}} = U \circ  \rhd  \circ  \mathrm {Cofree} :
   \mathrm {Fam}{\mathopen {}\left (\mathcal {C}\right )\mathclose {}} \to  \mathrm {Fam}{\mathopen {}\left (\mathcal {C}\right )\mathclose {}}.]]></fr:tex></html:p>
            <html:p>Concretely, later on families evaluates to
<fr:tex display="block"><![CDATA[\rhd _{\mathrm {Fam}} A\,{\mathopen {}\left (x\right )\mathclose {}} \;\cong \;
   \prod _{y \prec  x}\ \prod _{f : y \to  x} A{\mathopen {}\left (y\right )\mathclose {}}]]></fr:tex></html:p>
          </fr:mainmatter>
        </fr:tree>
